    "By drawing on this knowledge, we have formulated clear research objectives and devised appropriate research questions and search strategies Research ObjectivesThe Following are the research objectives of this study:• Evaluate the effectiveness of different chatbots, including ChatGPT, Google Bard, and Jasper Chat, in extracting biomarkers from diverse medical reports such as CT scans, pathology reports, and Electronic Health Records (EHR) notes.• Investigate the challenges associated with the implementation of chatbots for biomarker extraction in healthcare, focusing on data privacy, integration complexities, ethical considerations, and technical limitations, to provide a comprehensive understanding of the impediments in this domain.",
