    "These research questions are presented • How do different chatbots, namely ChatGPT, Google Bard, and Jasper Chat, compare in terms of their effectiveness in extracting biomarkers from various medical reports, including CT scans, pathology reports, and Electronic Health Records (EHR) notes?",
